programme.title: Hot Wives
programme.desc: When Natashas mother seduces her son-in-law, revenge sparks a chain of forbidden affairs, shocking pregnancies, and a family consumed by betrayal.

programme.title: The Sacrifice

programme.title: Chase To The Grave
programme.desc: From the moment King Malakai of Batibo kingdom slit kings Njaka throat, his soul was doomed for eternity. Now his only son pleads on his behalf as he tries to kill three queens.

programme.title: Lauretta
programme.desc: After Gina gives birth to Lauretta, she handed her to her elder sister so she can take care of her. The happy story ends when she get pregnant for her own child.

programme.title: Ikemba

programme.title: Family Collateral
programme.desc: Joy will cheat against her husband just to keep him alive from a dying ailment, this backfire as she gets pregnant in the process.

programme.title: Lies Men Tell
